column2: SELECT top #   m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1,    stack.ra AS ra, stack.dec  AS dec,    stack.has_wise_phot AS has_wise_phot,   stack.treated_as_pointsource AS treated_as_pointsource,   stack.w1_mag AS w1_mag,   stack.w1_mag_err AS w1_mag_err,   stack.w2_mag AS w2_mag,   stack.w2_mag_err AS w2_mag_err,   stack.w1_prochi2 AS w1_prochi2,   stack.w1_pronpix AS w1_pronpix,   stack.w1_profracflux AS w1_profracflux,   stack.w1_proflux AS w1_proflux,   stack.w1_npix AS w1_npix,   stack.w2_prochi2 AS w2_prochi2,   stack.w2_pronpix AS w2_pronpix,   stack.w2_profracflux AS w2_profracflux,   stack.w2_proflux AS w2_proflux,   stack.w2_npix AS w2_npix FROM MyDB.millionandhalftrainsam_radec AS m     OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n    LEFT JOIN wiseForcedTarget AS stack ON n.objid=stack.objID
